Ltd. (MRPL) , a unit of  India ’s largest explorer, is offering to sell
jet kerosene,  fuel oil  and mixed xylenes for October loading,
according to a document sent to potential buyers.  Details of the offer are:  Oil & Natural Gas Corp., the country’s largest oil
